body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, welcome to Quality Motors. My name is Jose Ramirez. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, Jose. My name is Heather Hall.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Heather. Before we continue, may I confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, I was born on the twentieth of March, nineteen eighty-five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Heather. Now, could you provide the first three digits of your home phone number?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Heather, for providing the information. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss today regarding our products or services?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, I'm just browsing for now. Everything seems great.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Fantastic to hear, Heather. Thank you for your time. Please feel free to reach out if you have any questions in the future. Have a wonderful day!
